    <h1>Accessibility (Content)</h1>
    <p class="description">Designing digital content — pages, posts, videos, emails — so people with disabilities can use it. Roughly <strong>16% of the world's population (1.3B people)</strong> live with a disability, so accessible content is both a legal and audience-size decision.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Marketing Head · theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
